{"tid":787254,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"韓系真係咁好睇咩","createTime":"2018-08-20T13:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T14:02:04.000Z","uid":195462,"like":22,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"952a7a641f7b99a47cbb86a8a8596899eb73ad1f","tid":787254,"uid":195462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"利申先: 唔係反韓撚<br />\n女:<br />\n空氣劉海<br />\n咩咩裙褲 高腰熱褲<br />\n白色露臍短T<br />\n2 or 3條間白襪<br />\n塊面有咁白得咁白<br />\n條唇有咁紅得咁紅<br />\n<br />\n女ge冇圖 梳<br />\n<br />\n男:<br />\n孿毛中分<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-mf-techbang.pixfs.net/system/images/37444/medium/8ce4e45749877f53a3d3ab5fe1b83169.jpg?1459236548\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-mf-techbang.pixfs.net%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F37444%2Fmedium%2F8ce4e45749877f53a3d3ab5fe1b83169.jpg%3F1459236548&h=670d69cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孿毛冬茹頭<br />\n大大粒黑色磁石夾耳珠<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shuaige5.com/d/file/20160922/1285a8be08fc1728d5b0a7f058fe97fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shuaige5.com%2Fd%2Ffile%2F20160922%2F1285a8be08fc1728d5b0a7f058fe97fc.jpg&h=5f289f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個頭七彩都算 有d係幾型幾靚<br />\n但有d真係不敢恭維<br />\n見過有條友個頭染到好似馬路邊倒洗碗水咁<br />\n上面個層反晒光ge油 又紫又藍又銀又綠<br />\n<br />\n又著棒球褸 有d中戴晒黑口罩<br />\n<br />\n人地國家都叫有棒球隊 有賽事<br />\n我們都冇 著黎為乜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n口罩你話廢氣多都算啦<br />\n但個d黑口罩又唔係即棄<br />\n好乾淨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n家陣出街D女8成都差唔多樣<br />\n你唔係韓國明星我都唔撚識分<br />\n我越黎越覺得自己面盲<br />\nD仔到底會唔會出街攬錯女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前D女就算mk得黎都哪有幾分清純feel<br />\n家陣好似個個人造人咁<br />\n就黎連D小學生出街打扮都冇清純feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9aa7029438931ed8d2001d8e210a62c952ba4d","tid":787254,"uid":154054,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"韓仔d頭只可以靚仔剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n柒頭剪只會加倍柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600c8bedef6a57415002c36ff0f8c8ac3294dd85","tid":787254,"uid":29093,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"港女 化 韓妝<br />\n效果好過<br />\n港仔 扮 韓仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26821e919a9b7c84256d8a8b152ef34e1254304","tid":787254,"uid":195462,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"8f9aa7029438931ed8d2001d8e210a62c952ba4d","tid":787254,"uid":154054,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"韓仔d頭只可以靚仔剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n柒頭剪只會加倍柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"如果單眼皮算靚仔一部份<br />\n其實我都係靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:同單眼皮冇乜分別ge內雙眼皮<br />\n但我都唔敢剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36b161ad1d61adf380d0e5c8958c97938a016cb","tid":787254,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},{"pid":"b6b2aeccf5af67386c9cdedf06264a2b69a29c15","tid":787254,"uid":74171,"like":4,"dislike":23,"score":-19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"咁好睇?<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/214508_f8fb08078e020c624070e